<div class="sub-content-header">ShowStoppers @ CES and Flooring Exhibits are NOT Affiliated with the International CES! </div>
<br />

It has recently come to our attention that many CES exhibitors are being contacted by ShowStoppers&nbsp;and Flooring Exhibits. <BR><BR>If you're asked to participate in&nbsp;ShowStoppers @ CES, please be advised that ShowStoppers has no connection with, nor is authorized by the International CES. We have received inquiries from exhibitors about the relationship and have formally asked Showstoppers to stop misleading companies by using the CES trademark. CES exhibitors spend a great deal of time and money to exhibit at CES and ShowStoppers is a distraction from the "core" reason for exhibitors to be in Las Vegas during January.<BR><BR>Also, if you are contacted by Flooring Exhibitsregarding ordering carpet for the International CES, please note that this company is not an official CES contractor and is not affiliated with or endorsed by CES. Here is a full listing of all official CES contractors at <A href="http://www.CESweb.org/manual">www.CESweb.org/manual</A>.
