<a name="3485"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Need Help Getting Your Best Customers to CES?</div>
<br />

<IMG hspace=5 align=right src="/images/photos/2010_Exhibitor_Invitation_72dpi.jpg" width=250 height=188>Use <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp#1925">CES exhibitor invitations</A> and invite your most important guests. This inexpensive, effective marketing tool allows your guests FREE advance registration to the International CES up until December 15, 2009. Or if they register on-site, they will save $100 on the $200 on-site registration fee. <BR><BR>You can either <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp#1925">download an electronic PDF</A> version of the invitations to send to your contacts via e-mail or order up to 1,000 printed invitations and we'll cover the print and production costs. Visit <A href="http://cesinvites.hbp.com/">cesinvites.hbp.com</A> for details and more information on how to personalize and mail your invitations. <BR><BR>Questions? Contact <A href="mailto:Invitations@CE.org">Invitations@CE.org</A> for more information. Don't miss this opportunity to invite your best customers to the 2010 International CES.
        <br /><img width="1" height="20" src="/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
