<a name="3484"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Secure Your Travel Visas Today!</div>
<br />

<IMG height=84 hspace=5 src="/images/photos/plane.jpg" width=125 align=right>If you are an exhibitor that requires a visa to enter the U.S., NOW is the time to request your letter of invitation and make your appointment for a visa interview. Wait times for a visa interview can be several weeks or more in many countries, especially during peak travel periods. With this in mind, we strongly urge you to register for CES and request a letter of invitation as soon as possible. For helpful tips on securing your visa, visit <A href="http://www.CESweb.org/International">CESweb.org/International</A>.<BR><BR>Also, a recent policy change requires all visitors to the U.S. from visa-waiver countries to register online and be authorized for entry as part of the new Electronic System for Travel Authorization program. <A href="http://www.dhs.gov/xnews/releases/pr_1212498415724.shtm" target=_blank>Learn more about this program</A>.
